1
00:01:35,052 --> 00:01:38,480
[Episode 15]

2
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,679
About Zhi Hua threatening you...

3
00:01:40,679 --> 00:01:42,080
We all know about it.

4
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:44,439
There is no antidote for Yemotian Poison.

5
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:47,560
Don't let Zhi Hua control you.

6
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,480
Hand him over.

7
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:51,239
Zhi Hua has no antidote at all.

8
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,719
Why do you still refuse to see reason?

9
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:55,912
I'm killing that damn official
not just for the antidote.

10
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,839
Hand over that damn official!

11
00:01:58,839 --> 00:02:02,052
You have a personal grudge
against the Magistrate of Yicheng?

12
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:10,359
If you don't reveal his whereabouts,
don't even think about leaving today!

13
00:02:10,359 --> 00:02:12,159
Bai Yu Tang, have you lost your mind?

14
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,439
Do you realize...

15
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:16,079
the cost of killing a court official?

16
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,840
People handle their own affairs.

17
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:21,079
Repay kindness, avenge wrongs.
I can accept any consequence!

18
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:24,079
Being so hesitant and fearful,
how can you call yourself a hero?

19
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,920
As for you, Lord Zhan,

20
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,759
the title of Imperial Cat has tamed you
just like that,

21
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:30,600
- stripping you of your martial spirit.
- That's too far!

22
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,479
Don't you know what kind of man Zhan is?

23
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:34,602
- For your sake, he--
- Miss Huo.

24
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:38,038
There's no need to say more.

25
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:44,527
If we must bare our hearts for him...

26
00:02:44,527 --> 00:02:47,466
to see the truth and tell friend from foe,

27
00:02:47,466 --> 00:02:49,439
then a friend like this...

28
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:52,275
I can do without!

29
00:02:52,959 --> 00:02:54,400
Miss Huo.

30
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:57,280
You don't need to intervene today.

31
00:02:57,280 --> 00:03:00,060
Let me settle this with him.

32
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:03,079
Now is not the time to be impulsive.

33
00:03:03,079 --> 00:03:04,480
Zhi Hua's men will be here any second.

34
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,940
Perfect timing.

35
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:10,952
They can serve as witnesses to our battle.

36
00:05:17,719 --> 00:05:18,960
Are you two finished fighting?

37
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,680
- No.
- No!

38
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,680
Then keep fighting until a winner is decided.

39
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:25,040
Let's go! To the back hill!

40
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,959
Bai Yu Tang.

41
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:10,120
I always thought you were smart.

42
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,279
I didn't expect you to be this foolish.

43
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:15,000
You're falling right into Zhi Hua's trap
without even realizing it.

44
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,439
Zhi Hua is clearly sowing dissension.

45
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,079
He wants us to fight each other first.

46
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,560
Then he can use you to do his dirty work,

47
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,600
and use you to get rid of
the Magistrate of Yicheng.

48
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,040
Can't you see that?

49
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,920
Of course I know what he's up to!

50
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,199
But I don't care!

51
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,839
As for using me,

52
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:31,040
as long as it's an evil man being killed,
what does it matter?

53
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,992
Let me ask you!

54
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,160
No matter how skilled you are,

55
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,920
can you slay all the evil in the world?

56
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,399
If you kill the Magistrate of Yicheng,

57
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:40,120
will Yu Lian and the others be saved?

58
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,879
Don't make it sound like
you're the only one who can save them!

59
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:45,519
Once I kill that damn official and Zhi Hua,

60
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:48,519
I will surely rescue Yu Lian!

61
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:51,160
If you charge in alone, who can you save?

62
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,959
Why should Yu Lian and the others
risk their lives with you?

63
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:56,802
Enough of your talk!

64
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,839
Bai Yu Tang.

65
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:40,040
You always say I'm trapped
by the title of Imperial Cat.

66
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,000
But who is the one

67
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,399
who truly cares about that title?

68
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:45,439
Who was it that caused a ruckus...

69
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:46,959
in the Bianjing city because of it?

70
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:48,480
You?

71
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:51,560
You're not worthy of mentioning the Five Rats!

72
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,652
The Five Rats?

73
00:07:53,652 --> 00:07:55,279
You Five Rats...

74
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:58,177
deserve to be kept in your place by me.

75
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,815
The Yemotian Poison has kicked in?

76
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:30,160
The cat-rat battle was truly spectacular.

77
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:33,560
It's a shame the Southern Knight
can no longer fight.

78
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:35,277
Bai Yu Tang.

79
00:08:35,277 --> 00:08:38,240
Let me finish this for you.

80
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:55,852
I wanted to avenge you.

81
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,639
But there are more important things to do
right now.

82
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:01,120
Excuses.

83
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:03,065
They're all excuses.

84
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:07,027
You never intended to avenge me.

85
00:09:11,199 --> 00:09:13,152
Bai Yu Tang!

86
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:29,079
If you really want to avenge me,

87
00:09:29,079 --> 00:09:31,490
kill him now!

88
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,039
Bai Yu Tang.

89
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:26,090
Wake up.

90
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,286
[Yanling]

91
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:34,010
Bai Yu Tang!

92
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,590
Zhan!

93
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:56,452
Let's go!

94
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:41,120
Master.

95
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,759
Zhan Zhao was heavily wounded
and fell off the cliff.

96
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,360
His chances of survival are slim.

97
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,480
Bai Yu Tang has also been
controlled by Yemotian Poison.

98
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,320
You can focus on organizing
your birthday banquet now.

99
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,720
Is this true?

100
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,840
Absolutely.

101
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,919
Zhan Zhao was killed by Bai Yu Tang.

102
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:55,368
I witnessed it with my own eyes.

103
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,320
Where is the body?

104
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,919
Since you say Zhan Zhao is dead,

105
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,759
why didn't you bring back the body?

106
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:04,360
The terrain where Zhan Zhao fell
is very treacherous.

107
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,519
Searching for him will be quite difficult.

108
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:08,000
The death soldiers are badly injured.

109
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:11,102
They need to rest before
they can take action again.

110
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:15,840
Father. Since Zhi Hua is making excuses,

111
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:19,243
let me lead some men
to search for Zhan Zhao's body.

112
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,815
Very well.

113
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,519
You've done a great service this time.

114
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:27,515
Go and get some rest first.

115
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:29,679
My injuries are nothing.

116
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,639
Now that Zhan Zhao is eliminated,

117
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:34,390
you can proceed with your plans.

118
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:40,290
Congratulations, Father.

119
00:12:40,290 --> 00:12:42,759
Once we close the net at the banquet,

120
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:45,377
you will rule the world.

121
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,732
We still cannot relax.

122
00:12:48,732 --> 00:12:51,879
Even though Zhan Zhao is no longer in the way,

123
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:55,159
we must still act with caution.

124
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:57,202
I understand.

125
00:13:18,079 --> 00:13:20,477
Any news?

126
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:24,160
But something seems fishy.

127
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:25,559
With Zhi Hua's skills alone,

128
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:28,120
how could he possibly kill Zhan Zhao?

129
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,839
Was the body seen?

130
00:13:30,839 --> 00:13:32,736
No.

131
00:13:35,439 --> 00:13:38,000
He Bo is headstrong.

132
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,959
No matter how many times he loses to Zhan Zhao,

133
00:13:40,959 --> 00:13:43,880
he never learns his lesson.

134
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,280
Indeed.

135
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:47,640
Without seeing Zhan Zhao's body,

136
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,880
how can we rest easy?

137
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:51,799
Let's wait and see for now.

138
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:54,040
The birthday banquet is approaching.

139
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:56,490
Keep a close eye on things.

140
00:13:56,490 --> 00:14:00,120
This isn't just about He Bo.

141
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:03,690
It concerns His Lordship's great cause.

142
00:15:19,199 --> 00:15:21,919
Don't make it sound like
you're the only one who can save them!

143
00:15:21,919 --> 00:15:24,559
Once I kill that damn official
and Zhi Hua,

144
00:15:24,559 --> 00:15:27,559
I will surely rescue Yu Lian!

145
00:15:27,559 --> 00:15:30,199
If you charge in alone,
who can you save?

146
00:15:30,199 --> 00:15:32,959
Why should Yu Lian and the others
risk their lives with you?

147
00:15:32,959 --> 00:15:35,815
Enough of your talk!

148
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:49,559
I have a plan.

149
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,959
I promise

150
00:15:50,959 --> 00:15:52,679
I will save everyone safely.

151
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:54,320
But I need your participation

152
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,199
to ensure nothing goes wrong.

153
00:15:56,199 --> 00:15:57,520
Once it's done,

154
00:15:57,520 --> 00:16:00,040
I'll take you
to the Magistrate of Yicheng.

155
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:02,552
Can you trust me just this once?

156
00:16:11,439 --> 00:16:13,640
What do you want me to do?

157
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:16,400
Since Zhi Hua wants to see
this Cat-Rat fight so badly,

158
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:18,402
so he can reap the benefits,

159
00:16:18,402 --> 00:16:22,165
why don't we just go with the flow?

160
00:16:32,679 --> 00:16:34,080
When we were acting,

161
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:36,909
was your poisoning real or an act?

162
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:39,719
Of course it was an act.

163
00:16:39,719 --> 00:16:42,340
Didn't you ask me to play along with your act?

164
00:16:47,959 --> 00:16:48,959
Shut up.

165
00:16:48,959 --> 00:16:51,190
Is it your turn to ask questions?

166
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:56,440
Why didn't you tell us
you were poisoned by Yemotian Poison?

167
00:17:00,319 --> 00:17:03,360
Weren't you the one
who said you wanted to part ways with me,

168
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:06,439
- and stay out of each other's business?
- Stop making excuses.

169
00:17:06,439 --> 00:17:08,605
You must have been poisoned when you
first scouted Zhongxiao Pavilion.

170
00:17:08,605 --> 00:17:11,040
- We hadn't parted ways then.
- That's enough.

171
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:13,559
Is Zhan really all right?

172
00:17:13,559 --> 00:17:14,920
The sword wound is no longer an issue.

173
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:17,319
But the residual poison is still there.

174
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:21,400
That day, when I heard Zhi Hua
had poisoned him, I checked his pulse.

175
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:24,080
His pulse was normal then,
no signs of poisoning.

176
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,853
The poison currently in his body has entered

177
00:17:25,853 --> 00:17:28,839
his meridians but not
his internal organs.

178
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:30,160
That's strange.

179
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,959
When my two sworn brothers were poisoned,

180
00:17:31,959 --> 00:17:33,612
in less than the time it takes
to drink a cup of tea,

181
00:17:33,612 --> 00:17:35,982
the poison reached their hearts.

182
00:17:37,690 --> 00:17:42,190
Hey, do you have some special constitution
that can suppress Yemotian Poison?

183
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,990
Take a guess.

184
00:17:54,079 --> 00:17:55,919
In another four hours,

185
00:17:55,919 --> 00:17:57,959
I can purge the remaining poison.

186
00:17:57,959 --> 00:17:59,680
Don't worry.

187
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,439
Then explain this.

188
00:18:01,439 --> 00:18:03,960
Why did you hide the fact
that you were poisoned?

189
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:05,960
Explain yourself.

190
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:10,559
Hiding it was my fault.

191
00:18:10,559 --> 00:18:12,319
But even though I'm at fault,

192
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:14,040
Bai Yu Tang is even more at fault.

193
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:15,847
Right?

194
00:18:16,679 --> 00:18:18,319
- You really are--
- You what?

195
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:23,452
Do you know how hard Zhan has tried to find
an antidote for your brothers these days?

196
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:27,652
The Young Master of the Tang Sect has
agreed to prepare the antidote for you.

197
00:18:27,652 --> 00:18:29,839
Just wait two more days.

198
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:32,615
Thank you.

199
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,079
That's it?

200
00:18:35,079 --> 00:18:36,919
People handle their own affairs.

201
00:18:36,919 --> 00:18:39,040
Repay kindness, avenge wrongs.

202
00:18:39,040 --> 00:18:42,702
Is this how you people show gratitude?

203
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,652
Thank you so much.

204
00:18:54,839 --> 00:18:56,790
Thank you very much.

205
00:18:59,079 --> 00:19:02,639
Your little play was quite a performance.

206
00:19:02,639 --> 00:19:04,639
I couldn't tell
if you were trying to fool Zhi Hua,

207
00:19:04,639 --> 00:19:06,427
or trying to mess with me.

208
00:19:06,427 --> 00:19:09,247
- We thought you heard everything.
- I did hear it.

209
00:19:09,247 --> 00:19:13,103
I heard exactly how you planned
to use your own lives as bait.

210
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:17,000
I only regret that I couldn't scold you both
right there.

211
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,119
Since you knew it was a plan,

212
00:19:18,119 --> 00:19:19,723
- then why did you--
- The injury was real.

213
00:19:19,723 --> 00:19:21,079
Falling off the cliff was also real.

214
00:19:21,079 --> 00:19:23,440
This plan was far too dangerous.

215
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:25,079
If the sword had been off by an inch,

216
00:19:25,079 --> 00:19:27,359
or if the Heavenward Crane Strike
hadn't protected you,

217
00:19:27,359 --> 00:19:30,070
wouldn't you really be dead?

218
00:19:34,079 --> 00:19:36,519
She's saying she was worried about you.

219
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:11,000
How did you find this place last night?

220
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:14,200
This wasn't part of the plan.

221
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:16,079
Didn't you both know I was coming all alone?

222
00:20:16,079 --> 00:20:18,720
Because I knew you'd be
worried about Zhan's safety,

223
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,440
so I specifically left plums for you.

224
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,799
I wasn't worried about him.

225
00:20:21,799 --> 00:20:23,359
The Moon Envoy was the worried one.

226
00:20:23,359 --> 00:20:26,119
She came to the secret room and
learned about the fake death plan.

227
00:20:26,119 --> 00:20:28,480
She feared he'd mess up the act
and end up as a dead cat for real.

228
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:31,852
So she let me out while Zhi Hua
was regulating his breathing.

229
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:38,490
The Moon Envoy would never
call Zhan a dead cat.

230
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,119
After being away for these days,

231
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:53,034
don't you have anything to say to us?

232
00:20:57,264 --> 00:20:58,777
I was reckless before. I'm sorry--

233
00:20:58,777 --> 00:21:00,400
- That's not it.
- Then what is it?

234
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,799
I want to know...

235
00:21:01,799 --> 00:21:04,790
how you've been these past few days.

236
00:21:11,799 --> 00:21:13,799
You're worried that your two sworn brothers...

237
00:21:13,799 --> 00:21:16,200
will be forced by Zhi Hua.

238
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,319
And you've done things against your will.

239
00:21:18,319 --> 00:21:20,902
You must be suffering inside.

240
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:26,720
But you're lucky you met the two of us.

241
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,526
With us by your side from now on,

242
00:21:28,526 --> 00:21:31,277
you won't have to suffer anymore.

243
00:21:32,527 --> 00:21:34,920
Why are you telling me this?

244
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,880
You're making me feel guilty.

245
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:39,365
That's exactly what I intended.

246
00:21:44,039 --> 00:21:45,960
Oh, right.

247
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,519
You said before...

248
00:21:47,519 --> 00:21:49,759
that you didn't kill the Magistrate
for the antidote.

249
00:21:49,759 --> 00:21:51,625
Then for what?

250
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:54,599
What else?

251
00:21:54,599 --> 00:21:58,680
I simply wanted to kill every one
of those villains in Xiangzhou.

252
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,359
If you had killed the Magistrate,

253
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:03,759
the stigma Zhan carries
would be very hard to clear.

254
00:22:03,759 --> 00:22:06,079
And you would become a wanted criminal.

255
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:08,975
You knew the consequences.

256
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:13,759
Zhan Zhao should have been
a hero roaming the world.

257
00:22:13,759 --> 00:22:15,519
So what if he carries the stigma?

258
00:22:15,519 --> 00:22:17,599
So what if he's a wanted criminal?

259
00:22:17,599 --> 00:22:21,720
If they still won't let him go,
I'll kill everyone who comes after him.

260
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,559
As for me...

261
00:22:23,559 --> 00:22:28,160
the court can't use a piece of paper
to define whether I'm a hero or a bandit.

262
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:32,079
They didn't give me justice 15 years ago.

263
00:22:32,079 --> 00:22:36,014
Now, I'll take it back with my own hands.

264
00:22:36,799 --> 00:22:38,960
15 years ago?

265
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:41,080
What happened then?

266
00:22:43,760 --> 00:22:45,279
Why isn't Zhan Zhao out yet?

267
00:22:45,279 --> 00:22:47,415
I'll go check on him.

268
00:22:57,799 --> 00:23:00,000
So he was already fine when you came out.

269
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,319
And you didn't even tell me.

270
00:23:01,319 --> 00:23:03,627
You didn't ask.

271
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:06,079
Fine.

272
00:23:06,079 --> 00:23:07,720
It's about time.

273
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,560
I should go back and play my part as a puppet.

274
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:12,120
When do we strike, Lord Zhan?

275
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:16,599
Finish what you were saying first.

276
00:23:16,599 --> 00:23:19,340
Then we'll tell you the rest of the plan.

277
00:23:20,639 --> 00:23:22,480
We just didn't want you to be bored,

278
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,680
so we wanted you to speak your mind.

279
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,200
Since you're not willing to talk...

280
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,319
then so be it.

281
00:23:27,319 --> 00:23:29,879
As for the rest of the plan, that depends on...

282
00:23:29,879 --> 00:23:33,477
how the Jing family's birthday banquet
preparation goes.

283
00:23:54,319 --> 00:23:56,440
My Lord, you've been in a good mood lately.

284
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:59,200
I've specially had some wine warmed up.

285
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:02,512
Have a good rest this afternoon.

286
00:24:03,159 --> 00:24:06,319
You've really changed your tune today.

287
00:24:06,319 --> 00:24:09,879
It's rare to hear you speak to me so kindly.

288
00:24:09,879 --> 00:24:13,079
Well, your birthday banquet is coming up soon.

289
00:24:13,079 --> 00:24:14,839
I'm happy for you too.

290
00:24:14,839 --> 00:24:17,359
I'll warm up some hangover soup for you.

291
00:24:17,359 --> 00:24:19,820
You can drink it when you wake up.

292
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,160
The mountain path is steep and muddy.

293
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,079
Don't be impatient and take shortcuts.

294
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:48,879
Taking the main road will do.

295
00:24:48,879 --> 00:24:50,200
Once the operation begins,

296
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:52,680
He Bo will focus on you.

297
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:55,127
You must protect yourself.

298
00:24:56,427 --> 00:24:59,027
Only then can we be at ease.

299
00:24:59,027 --> 00:25:00,639
Don't worry.

300
00:25:00,639 --> 00:25:02,119
You always agree so quickly,

301
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:04,652
but following through is a different story.

302
00:25:08,559 --> 00:25:11,602
Alright, I'm leaving. Wait for me.

303
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:36,520
Keep this for me for now.

304
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,765
Give it back to me when I return.

305
00:25:40,799 --> 00:25:45,240
You must never risk your life like that.

306
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,865
Alright.

307
00:25:47,865 --> 00:25:49,490
I'm off.

308
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:26,680
Commander Shao.

309
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,165
Have you found Ling Long?

310
00:26:28,165 --> 00:26:29,200
Not yet.

311
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:32,159
The rain was too heavy last night,
washing away all the footprints.

312
00:26:32,159 --> 00:26:35,271
It's very difficult to find Miss Huo's trail.

313
00:26:35,839 --> 00:26:37,927
What about the Jing Mansion?

314
00:26:37,927 --> 00:26:39,319
Nothing unusual.

315
00:26:39,319 --> 00:26:41,200
They are preparing for the birthday banquet.

316
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,200
They also sent men to look for Zhan Zhao.

317
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:45,200
Zhi Hua hasn't made a move.

318
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:47,725
He should still be in Zhongxiao Pavilion.

319
00:26:48,359 --> 00:26:50,352
Keep watching then.

320
00:26:50,352 --> 00:26:55,940
[The Jing Mansion]

321
00:27:13,119 --> 00:27:15,165
Stop! Stop! Stop!

322
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,920
Who are you people?

323
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:24,821
My Lord.
They are here to tailor new clothes for Madam.

324
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:46,790
I asked them to come.

325
00:27:57,879 --> 00:27:59,080
It's almost dark.

326
00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:01,879
Why are you inviting tailors now, Mother?

327
00:28:01,879 --> 00:28:03,440
Lord Jing's birthday is coming up.

328
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:06,839
If I don't start now,
I won't be ready in time to wear.

329
00:28:06,839 --> 00:28:10,159
If you have time, come with me to be measured.

330
00:28:10,159 --> 00:28:12,952
I'll have a few new outfits made for you too.

331
00:28:12,952 --> 00:28:16,040
Thank you, Mother, but that's necessary.

332
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:18,740
Then I'll take them inside first.

333
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:24,440
You.

334
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:26,119
Bring this chest to my room later.

335
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:27,527
Yes, sir.

336
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:43,240
Take them to the storeroom
to pick out the fabrics first.

337
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:46,160
The rest of you, follow me to be measured.

338
00:28:55,359 --> 00:28:58,079
Thank you for your help, Mrs. Jing.

339
00:28:58,079 --> 00:29:00,040
At noon, I took advantage
of Jing Yi Ming's good mood,

340
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,565
and urged him to have a few more drinks.

341
00:29:01,565 --> 00:29:03,801
He should be asleep by now. We must hurry.

342
00:29:03,801 --> 00:29:05,319
Thank you, Mrs. Jing.

343
00:29:05,319 --> 00:29:07,002
Let's go.

344
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,240
I'm here to get you out.

345
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,599
I know you.

346
00:29:32,599 --> 00:29:35,640
You're the one who fought He Bo
in the secret room last time.

347
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:38,359
Follow me closely. I'll get you out of here.

348
00:29:38,359 --> 00:29:41,640
No matter what happens, do not be afraid.

349
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:48,315
Put this on.

350
00:29:52,359 --> 00:29:54,720
What do you think of my skills?

351
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:56,440
Your skills are excellent.

352
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,399
Even He Bo is a bit afraid of you.

353
00:29:58,399 --> 00:29:59,680
In that case,

354
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:01,280
set your mind at ease.

355
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:03,402
I will definitely get you out.

356
00:30:05,359 --> 00:30:06,877
Okay.

357
00:30:13,879 --> 00:30:16,079
Yu Lian, go.

358
00:30:16,079 --> 00:30:17,639
Once you leave this manor,

359
00:30:17,639 --> 00:30:19,680
you'll never have to fear Jing Yi Ming anymore.

360
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:23,215
Madam, please come with me.

361
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:25,879
I still have unfinished business.

362
00:30:25,879 --> 00:30:27,599
- Mrs. Jing...
- Don't worry.

363
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:30,559
I have my own ways to deal with Jing Yi Ming.

364
00:30:30,559 --> 00:30:33,680
Once you make his crimes public,

365
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:36,440
I can leave with the girls
from Zhongxiao Pavilion...

366
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:38,240
with dignity...

367
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:40,765
and leave this place openly.

368
00:30:40,765 --> 00:30:42,040
Yu Lian.

369
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:44,399
When the dust settles,

370
00:30:44,399 --> 00:30:47,280
you must forget everything here.

371
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:51,059
And pursue your own carefree life.

372
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,280
Don't cry.

373
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:54,359
Go now.

374
00:30:54,359 --> 00:30:55,880
You can't delay any longer.

375
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:57,720
Go, go, go.

376
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:59,040
Go!

377
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,359
Mrs. Jing,

378
00:31:00,359 --> 00:31:02,415
please take care.

379
00:31:29,079 --> 00:31:30,877
Master.

380
00:31:33,559 --> 00:31:35,059
Father.

381
00:31:35,639 --> 00:31:38,077
Get out! All of you, get out!

382
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:44,960
Father. Shao Ji Zu's men sent word.

383
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,635
They said Zhan Zhao's body was never found.

384
00:31:46,635 --> 00:31:47,640
I haven't found it either.

385
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,039
This is likely a trick.

386
00:31:49,039 --> 00:31:51,359
I knew Zhi Hua wasn't that capable.

387
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:52,600
We were indeed fooled!

388
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:54,800
Is this the time to gloat?

389
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:56,200
Order the manor to be sealed now!

390
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,880
Yes, sir.

391
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:01,480
Why are you following me?

392
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:02,960
Go inform Zhi Hua immediately!

393
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:04,920
Bai Yu Tang must have been faking it.

394
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,725
Yes, sir.

395
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:09,759
They caught us.

396
00:32:09,759 --> 00:32:11,760
We've been spotted.

397
00:32:11,760 --> 00:32:13,465
Yu Lian,

398
00:32:13,465 --> 00:32:16,340
did you forget what Mrs. Jing just said?

399
00:32:41,079 --> 00:32:43,487
Looking for me?

400
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,911
You weren't poisoned?

401
00:32:50,559 --> 00:32:54,952
Keeping my neck stiff like that
was exhausting for me.

402
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,065
Looking for this?

403
00:33:02,839 --> 00:33:05,107
Kill Zhi Hua!

404
00:33:37,799 --> 00:33:39,515
Wait.

405
00:33:44,927 --> 00:33:46,480
How come only the two of you came out?

406
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:48,326
Where are the other three?

407
00:34:13,040 --> 00:34:16,520
Zhi Hua, you can't hold a grudge
like your Master Bai.

408
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:20,440
How do you like the taste of your own poison?

409
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:24,720
Though these people were greedy
and tried to learn every sect's skills,

410
00:34:24,720 --> 00:34:26,520
that they fell into your trap.

411
00:34:26,520 --> 00:34:31,224
But there's no need for them
to die for pieces of trash like you.

412
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:35,730
Stop!

413
00:34:42,559 --> 00:34:44,079
It's about time.

414
00:34:44,079 --> 00:34:47,840
Zhi Hua. We'll settle our score here for today.

415
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:51,627
But this isn't over between us.

416
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:26,159
This is My Lord's favorite tune.

417
00:35:26,159 --> 00:35:28,240
Since Yu Lian is no longer here,

418
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:31,227
I shall play it for him instead.

419
00:35:33,559 --> 00:35:36,502
Do you think I won't dare to kill you?

420
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:42,559
Kill me?

421
00:35:42,559 --> 00:35:44,927
You wouldn't dare.

422
00:35:44,927 --> 00:35:48,193
Back then, you used others to kill
and wipe out my Bawang Manor.

423
00:35:48,193 --> 00:35:50,960
Then you hypocritically married me.

424
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:56,826
Wasn't it just to build a reputation
in the world for saving me from misery?

425
00:35:57,520 --> 00:36:01,000
Furthermore, the birthday banquet is imminent.

426
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,680
If you kill me,

427
00:36:02,680 --> 00:36:05,882
how will you explain it to the guests?

428
00:36:05,882 --> 00:36:08,800
Ever since your previous wife
was driven to her death by you,

429
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:11,639
there have been many rumors out there.

430
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:15,360
Your long-planned great cause
is about to succeed.

431
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:18,702
Why would you risk any complications?

432
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:22,000
My Lady, you truly know me best.

433
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:24,000
After the birthday banquet,

434
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,239
you will take Yu Lian's place...

435
00:36:26,239 --> 00:36:29,680
and stay in this dark room forever,
playing music for me.

436
00:36:29,680 --> 00:36:33,159
I want you to see with your own eyes
how those nobodies

437
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:37,159
use Bawang Manor's Dragon Roar Swordplay
to kill people!

438
00:36:37,159 --> 00:36:39,251
Guards!

439
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:44,840
Any news on Zhi Hua?

440
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:46,719
Master, Zhi Hua went to Fenglai Pavilion.

441
00:36:46,719 --> 00:36:49,080
He hasn't returned yet.

442
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:50,480
Seal off the entire mansion immediately!

443
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:53,319
If Yu Lian escapes, everyone's head will roll!

444
00:36:53,319 --> 00:36:56,065
- Send men to keep a close watch on her.
- Yes, sir.

445
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:39,377
If you can't bring back Bai Yu Tang,

446
00:37:39,377 --> 00:37:42,397
I'll slaughter Chang Hong Bi tonight.

447
00:37:45,119 --> 00:37:48,227
Are you blind? Can't you see I'm right here?

448
00:37:51,599 --> 00:37:54,600
Master Zhi always talks big
in front of my father.

449
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:57,119
But when it comes to actually
getting things done,

450
00:37:57,119 --> 00:38:00,602
one might think you're in league with them.

451
00:38:02,119 --> 00:38:04,040
I've been working myself to the bone,

452
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:07,440
while you've done nothing but slack off.
And now you're here making sarcastic remarks.

453
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:09,440
You're just a bastard child.

454
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:12,547
How dare you put on airs before me,
the future sect master?

455
00:38:14,279 --> 00:38:15,551
I'll tell you the truth.

456
00:38:15,551 --> 00:38:17,440
Father told me everything.

457
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:20,040
No matter how well you master
the Great Compassion Palm,

458
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:23,111
he will still have me inherit
the mantle of the Shangqing Sect.

459
00:38:23,679 --> 00:38:26,480
Now that you've caused such a disaster,

460
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:29,080
how can you have the nerve to compete with me?

461
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:31,727
You overconfident half-breed!

462
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:36,263
You should take a good look at yourself.

463
00:38:37,759 --> 00:38:39,402
Zhi Hua.

464
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:14,520
How did it go? Did you succeed?

465
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:17,000
She's asking you. Did you succeed?

466
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:19,640
Zhao Hui has already taken her back.

467
00:39:22,159 --> 00:39:23,199
Don't worry.

468
00:39:23,199 --> 00:39:24,599
Your brother is fine.

469
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:25,679
What?

470
00:39:25,679 --> 00:39:27,527
Brother?

471
00:39:31,759 --> 00:39:34,215
You still don't want to reunite?

472
00:39:47,199 --> 00:39:49,239
Yue Hua?

473
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:50,840
Bai.

474
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:53,719
Forgive me for hiding the truth.

475
00:39:53,719 --> 00:39:55,319
Zhan.

476
00:39:55,319 --> 00:39:59,920
The day we met, you were playing the tune
Father taught us as children.

477
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:02,102
I knew then that you recognized me.

478
00:40:02,102 --> 00:40:05,520
The reason I didn't acknowledge you
was because...

479
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:08,920
I didn't want to admit
that while you were seriously injured,

480
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:10,880
I was the one who tried to kill you.

481
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,759
I understand.

482
00:40:12,759 --> 00:40:14,199
You had no choice.

483
00:40:14,199 --> 00:40:15,920
Look at me now.

484
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,639
Aren't I perfectly fine?

485
00:40:17,639 --> 00:40:18,913
Miss Yue Hua.

486
00:40:18,913 --> 00:40:20,692
You're truly remarkable now.

487
00:40:20,692 --> 00:40:23,440
When there's a chance,
I must have a proper spar with you.

488
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:26,715
To improve so much in just one year,

489
00:40:27,319 --> 00:40:29,520
you must have endured much hardship.

490
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:31,360
Your brother, Zhao Hui, is with us.

491
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,880
Do you want to go see him?

492
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,360
Of course you do.

493
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:37,639
- Zhao Hui would be so happy--
- No, I cannot see him.

494
00:40:37,639 --> 00:40:39,319
I hid in the Hanshui Palace.

495
00:40:39,319 --> 00:40:41,599
I even became a guard dog
at the Zhongxiao Pavilion,

496
00:40:41,599 --> 00:40:44,565
just for the chance to kill Jing Yi Ming.

497
00:40:44,565 --> 00:40:46,719
My task is not yet finished.

498
00:40:46,719 --> 00:40:48,080
I cannot give up halfway.

499
00:40:48,080 --> 00:40:49,920
Yue Hua.

500
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:51,960
If you face Jing Yi Ming alone,

501
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:54,199
you have no chance of winning.

502
00:40:54,199 --> 00:40:55,719
The case he's involved in is massive.

503
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:57,679
You are not the only one...

504
00:40:57,679 --> 00:41:00,480
whose blood is on his hands.

505
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,960
Leave him to me.

506
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:03,040
No.

507
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,400
I swore an oath.

508
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,360
That I would kill Jing Yi Ming myself.

509
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:09,560
Just pretend you never saw me.

510
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:11,402
Yue Hua!

511
00:41:11,402 --> 00:41:12,880
Let her go.

512
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:16,400
Even if she wants revenge,
she won't be reckless enough to go today.

513
00:41:16,400 --> 00:41:18,590
We'll have another chance to persuade her.

514
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:43,239
Who did this?

515
00:41:43,239 --> 00:41:45,040
Bai Yu Tang.

516
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:48,719
You have so many men under you.

517
00:41:48,719 --> 00:41:53,480
How could he kill Xing Ze on my turf
and still manage to escape?

518
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,702
Please calm down, Master.

519
00:41:55,702 --> 00:41:57,440
When Bai Yu Tang...

520
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:58,920
came to cause trouble earlier,

521
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:01,119
I realized...

522
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:03,599
he was using a feint to distract me,

523
00:42:03,599 --> 00:42:05,880
allowing Zhan Zhao to rescue.

524
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:08,119
I wanted to take men back to the manor
to provide reinforcements,

525
00:42:08,119 --> 00:42:09,840
but...

526
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,679
But Xing Ze refused to listen.

527
00:42:12,679 --> 00:42:16,534
He insisted on capturing Bai Yu Tang
as a birthday gift for you.

528
00:42:22,719 --> 00:42:25,390
Go and do two things immediately.

529
00:42:25,390 --> 00:42:26,960
First,

530
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:29,400
have Shao Ji Zu inform the county office.

531
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:32,719
Set up checkpoints at all four gates.
Do not let Zhan Zhao and the others escape!

532
00:42:32,719 --> 00:42:34,080
- Yes.
- At the same time,

533
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:37,279
have him lead a full search of Xiangyang
to find Yu Lian.

534
00:42:37,279 --> 00:42:39,819
He knows the gravity of this matter,
so he won't refuse.

535
00:42:39,819 --> 00:42:41,279
Second,

536
00:42:41,279 --> 00:42:44,319
All the girls and the death soldiers
at the Zhongxiao Pavilion...

537
00:42:44,319 --> 00:42:45,360
take a full tally!

538
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:47,094
Yes, sir.
